# Example: Gate Window Release

After a successful commit:

```text
WAKE ScarletOwl: commit abc1234 is pushed and GATE-WINDOW is released. Your
lexicon plan landing is next. Confirm index empty before staging.
```

The matching mail includes:

- commit hash
- attestation path
- pushed state
- released reservation ids or release time
- known unstaged dirt that does not belong to the next owner
